WEBVTT

00:35.167 --> 00:37.833
Lotte Entertainment
& Dexter Studios Present

00:51.833 --> 00:54.417
A Realies Pictures
& Dexter Studios Production

01:12.208 --> 01:14.833
Original Story by Ju ho-min

01:17.667 --> 01:20.768
When a person reaches
the afterlife,

01:20.792 --> 01:25.143
one is judged 7 times
over the course of 49 days.

01:25.167 --> 01:31.184
Tried by deceit, indolence, injustice
betrayal, violence, murder, filial impiety,

01:31.208 --> 01:35.851
only the souls who pass
all trials are reincarnated.

01:35.875 --> 01:40.083
Buddhist Scripture

01:45.458 --> 01:48.292
Ha Jung-woo

01:49.458 --> 01:53.000
Cha Tae-hyun

01:54.167 --> 01:57.000
Ju Ji-hoon

01:58.167 --> 02:00.958
Kim Hyang-qi

02:02.125 --> 02:04.917
and Lee Jung-jae

02:42.167 --> 02:45.542
Written and Directed by Kim Yong-hwa

03:03.083 --> 03:04.000
Kim!

03:05.292 --> 03:06.292
Take my hand!

03:06.833 --> 03:08.417
Give me the kid!
Grab my hand!

03:09.417 --> 03:10.417
Come on!

03:10.875 --> 03:11.875
Reach out your hand!

03:13.625 --> 03:14.625
Hurry!

03:15.625 --> 03:17.125
The rope!
It's on fire!

03:17.875 --> 03:18.875
Take my hand!

03:19.292 --> 03:19.976
No!

03:20.000 --> 03:21.125
Ja-hong! No!

03:41.625 --> 03:42.875
We made it, we're alive.

03:43.208 --> 03:44.542
It's okay, sweetie.

03:45.042 --> 03:46.042
Mom!

03:47.167 --> 03:48.167
Mom!

03:50.792 --> 03:52.667
Hey! Get over here!

03:57.667 --> 03:58.958
That was close!

03:59.875 --> 04:01.250
That could've ended badly!

04:02.167 --> 04:04.750
Little lady, what's your name?

04:05.292 --> 04:06.292
Kim Ja-hong!

04:06.833 --> 04:08.643
That's my name, cutie.

04:08.667 --> 04:10.625
How did you know my name?

04:11.083 --> 04:12.333
What's yours?

04:13.333 --> 04:14.333
Your name...

04:14.958 --> 04:16.416
Kim Ja-hong!

04:19.375 --> 04:20.541
Kim Ja-hong!

05:02.250 --> 05:03.500
You there!

05:03.833 --> 05:06.333
Get out of there!
It's dangerous!

05:06.792 --> 05:08.875
Get a stretcher!
Hurry the hell up!

05:09.000 --> 05:10.167
Ja-hong!

05:10.417 --> 05:11.393
Mr. Kim Ja-hong!

05:11.417 --> 05:12.417
Wow!

05:13.833 --> 05:17.768
How the hell did you think
to jump from there?

05:17.792 --> 05:21.708
You fell from such height,
and honorably saved a girl...

05:22.542 --> 05:24.059
A paragon!

05:24.083 --> 05:27.167
The last honorable death
was 422 years ago.

05:27.583 --> 05:29.000
I am honored,
Mr. Kim Ja-hong!

05:29.458 --> 05:31.792
The last one was Nongae in 1592.

05:32.333 --> 05:33.333
He's a paragon?

05:36.042 --> 05:41.268
You passed away on
April 28, 2017 as scheduled.

05:41.292 --> 05:44.434
We are 3 guardians
of the afterlife,

05:44.458 --> 05:49.083
who will defend you
through 7 trials over 49 days.

05:49.875 --> 05:52.375
I'm a security specialist
Deputy Guardian Hewonmak.

05:53.833 --> 05:56.518
I am Assistant Guardian
Deok-choon.

05:56.542 --> 05:57.684
Good to meet you!

05:57.708 --> 05:59.125
It's an honor, sir!

06:01.125 --> 06:03.768
We said 3 guardians,
so why just 2?

06:03.792 --> 06:05.393
It's an obvious question.

06:05.417 --> 06:06.833
The last guardian is...

06:07.083 --> 06:08.833
At your funeral home.

06:09.333 --> 06:12.934
It's a protocol,
but I think he went for food.

06:12.958 --> 06:14.458
He's a strange one,
don't you think?

06:14.958 --> 06:17.476
Mr. Kim?
What's up?

06:17.500 --> 06:21.143
Everything's fine,
you're a death virgin.

06:21.167 --> 06:23.792
That's why it's confusing
and awkward.

06:24.750 --> 06:25.750
No...

06:26.958 --> 06:28.542
I can't die just yet.

06:29.042 --> 06:30.042
My mother...

06:31.417 --> 06:33.000
I can't leave my mother!

06:33.500 --> 06:35.434
Afterlife law, article 3.1!

06:35.458 --> 06:39.684
One can't wander the living world,
and no time for farewells!

06:39.708 --> 06:43.809
If you plead the fifth,
you'll be in a disadvantage...

06:43.833 --> 06:46.768
He's following the protocol
like a real paragon.

06:46.792 --> 06:48.434
Good, keep going!

06:48.458 --> 06:51.875
Up! Up!

06:53.125 --> 06:56.434
Then let me see my mother
one last time, please!

06:56.458 --> 06:57.976
I have something to tell her!

06:58.000 --> 06:59.976
Love for his mother...

07:00.000 --> 07:01.417
Please, I'm begging you!

07:04.000 --> 07:05.292
One last time!

07:06.708 --> 07:07.958
Please!

07:32.792 --> 07:34.167
This is bad even for me.

07:42.208 --> 07:45.458
Casketing for Kim Ja-hong
will begin shortly.

07:46.167 --> 07:51.292
Once again, casketing for
Kim Ja-hong will begin shortly.

07:53.125 --> 07:54.125
Mom.

07:55.292 --> 07:56.292
Mom?

07:58.125 --> 08:00.125
Snap out of it, Mom.

08:02.208 --> 08:04.083
He's ready, let's go.

08:08.000 --> 08:11.792
Mom, we should go!

08:31.250 --> 08:34.625
Gate of Afterlife

08:42.250 --> 08:43.250
Salute!

08:43.832 --> 08:45.851
That's King Yeomra.

08:45.875 --> 08:48.458
The judge of Filial Impiety Hell,
and the king of kings.

08:49.125 --> 08:52.101
And he's guardian gang-hm.

08:52.125 --> 08:54.559
The leader and our boss.

08:54.583 --> 08:58.958
He reincarnated 47 souls
in the past century.

08:59.458 --> 09:02.292
Paragon Kim, good to meet you.
Make way for a paragon!

09:04.083 --> 09:05.333
I'm not a paragon.

09:08.292 --> 09:09.292
Over here!

09:09.708 --> 09:10.684
Here! Here!

09:10.708 --> 09:12.393
Let him through.
Make way.

09:12.417 --> 09:14.458
Mr. Kim, please hurry!
Make way.

09:20.042 --> 09:22.042
Kim Ja-hong

09:33.125 --> 09:35.125
Incredible! He's the one!

09:37.083 --> 09:40.333
Mr. Kim, you really are
an honorable paragon!

09:40.792 --> 09:42.393
It's been 19 years!

09:42.417 --> 09:46.809
Your chance of reincarnation
after 49 days is very high!

09:46.833 --> 09:49.417
An honorable soul!
Paragon Kim Ja-hong!

10:05.208 --> 10:06.957
Volcano of the damned

10:06.958 --> 10:08.582
volcano of the damned why the hell
is murder hell our first stop?

10:08.583 --> 10:09.542
Why the hell is
murder hell our first stop?

10:11.167 --> 10:13.143
Murder hell! The volcano!

10:13.167 --> 10:15.768
You said he's a paragon.

10:15.792 --> 10:18.375
Did you really kill someone?

10:19.000 --> 10:20.000
What?

10:21.292 --> 10:23.167
I didn't kill anyone.

10:23.792 --> 10:26.976
There are a total of 7 trials...

10:27.000 --> 10:30.143
Betrayal, violence, filial impiety,
murder, indolence, deceit, injustice.

10:30.167 --> 10:33.893
King Yeomra assigns
the trial order

10:33.917 --> 10:37.208
starting from a light sin
to a heavy sin.

10:38.792 --> 10:40.309
Other than Yeomra,

10:40.333 --> 10:43.250
no one knows the order
of your trials.

10:43.500 --> 10:46.726
Murder? I've never
harmed anyone.

10:46.750 --> 10:49.476
This trial will also
look at indirect murders.

10:49.500 --> 10:52.684
If your past actions
influenced someone's death,

10:52.708 --> 10:55.083
that is enough cause
to be charged.

10:55.375 --> 10:57.976
So don't post mean
comments online hastily!

10:58.000 --> 10:59.143
It's all recorded!

10:59.167 --> 11:01.667
No need to worry,
guess what she's doing.

11:03.750 --> 11:05.976
Our baby has a special power.

11:06.000 --> 11:09.018
She's scanning
a list of all your charges,

11:09.042 --> 11:12.143
to better defend you.

11:12.167 --> 11:14.601
It may seem like a skill
but it's like Karma.

11:14.625 --> 11:15.792
It must be taxing on her.

11:16.458 --> 11:17.458
Who did he kill?

11:46.750 --> 11:47.750
No!

11:50.625 --> 11:51.875
Sir!

11:58.667 --> 12:02.250
Murder Hell

12:17.458 --> 12:18.458
Give me your hand!

12:21.000 --> 12:22.000
Just a little more!

12:22.208 --> 12:23.125
I got you!

12:23.958 --> 12:24.809
Climb!

12:24.833 --> 12:26.792
You insolent prick!

12:27.000 --> 12:29.042
How dare you!

12:36.958 --> 12:39.458
God of Murder

12:49.167 --> 12:54.851
This trial is about leaving
a doomed colleague behind

12:54.875 --> 12:57.309
despite having enough time,

12:57.333 --> 13:00.934
Kim's desire for his own safety
and indecisiveness

13:00.958 --> 13:04.417
caused his colleague's death.

13:08.833 --> 13:14.018
If he acted in time,
the victim could've survived,

13:14.042 --> 13:19.375
therefore, this could be
seen as an indirect murder!

13:25.625 --> 13:29.601
This indirect murder was

13:29.625 --> 13:33.143
a direct result of
his willful negligence,

13:33.167 --> 13:37.684
and he must suffer
in the volcano

13:37.708 --> 13:39.000
for 50 years...

13:40.333 --> 13:41.184
5 years!

13:41.208 --> 13:43.292
You can't demand
50 years from a paragon!

13:44.208 --> 13:46.101
He's a paragon!

13:46.125 --> 13:48.208
Be respectful with your demands!

13:49.500 --> 13:51.333
We demand a punishment

13:52.500 --> 13:55.809
of 5 years that feels like 50!

13:55.833 --> 13:57.958
Because he's a paragon!

14:02.000 --> 14:04.458
Guardians, begin your defense!

14:08.500 --> 14:10.625
I'd like to first ask the defendant.

14:11.667 --> 14:15.292
Do you remember your
colleague's last words?

14:21.708 --> 14:22.708
Hello?!

14:24.542 --> 14:25.684
Listen.
Help!

14:25.708 --> 14:26.976
Help the injured first.

14:27.000 --> 14:29.768
It'll be safer
if you control the fire.

14:29.792 --> 14:33.434
Puncture the outer wall
and lift this with a pulley.

14:33.458 --> 14:34.458
Got it?

14:35.875 --> 14:38.708
It might cave in, get going!

14:39.375 --> 14:40.375
Get out!

14:41.000 --> 14:41.643
Go on!

14:41.667 --> 14:44.268
I'll be back shortly.

14:44.292 --> 14:45.351
Stay right here!

14:45.375 --> 14:47.851
That's all I can do.

14:47.875 --> 14:49.625
I'll be right here.

14:53.458 --> 14:55.542
Here, take this.

14:58.542 --> 14:59.667
You'll need it!

15:03.625 --> 15:05.083
Go! Go on!

15:11.958 --> 15:14.375
Kim Ja-hong, raise your head.

15:15.625 --> 15:16.792
You're not guilty yet.

15:18.167 --> 15:19.667
Raise your head, Mr. Kim.

15:25.375 --> 15:26.875
One more question.

15:27.708 --> 15:30.059
During the fire that day,

15:30.083 --> 15:35.059
you followed his order
and couldn't save him,

15:35.083 --> 15:37.125
but how many others
have you saved?

15:40.458 --> 15:41.500
6...

15:42.958 --> 15:43.958
7?

15:45.125 --> 15:49.000
I'm not sure,
I can't remember...

15:53.167 --> 15:54.917
Please pay attention
to the mirror of Karma.

16:00.625 --> 16:01.750
May I borrow this?

16:10.458 --> 16:11.934
As you can see,

16:11.958 --> 16:16.726
his memory may be foggy,
but he saved exactly 8 lives

16:16.750 --> 16:19.476
from the vicious inferno.

16:19.500 --> 16:23.125
He was on the nightly news
for his heroism.

16:24.167 --> 16:26.809
Let me ask you this.

16:26.833 --> 16:30.393
The defendant saved
8 total strangers,

16:30.417 --> 16:34.708
but in doing so,
he couldn't save his colleague.

16:35.458 --> 16:38.684
Then how are these lives
weighed differently?

16:38.708 --> 16:40.125
I await your answer.

16:46.500 --> 16:48.333
Such nonsense
on the first trial?

16:48.667 --> 16:52.934
How do you weigh lives?
They're not even tangible.

16:52.958 --> 16:57.250
If something invisible
has weight, they're all the same...

17:08.708 --> 17:10.083
Honorable god of murder,

17:10.625 --> 17:16.226
please take into consideration
the prosecutor's last statement,

17:16.250 --> 17:21.625
as you weigh in on
honorable Kim's charges.

17:27.083 --> 17:29.309
It's too dangerous!
Get back!

17:29.333 --> 17:31.101
Don't go!

17:31.125 --> 17:33.042
No! No!

17:37.292 --> 17:38.625
My daughter...

17:40.833 --> 17:43.625
Ji-yeon, my baby!

18:11.250 --> 18:13.125
Here is my final verdict!

18:14.125 --> 18:17.559
The defendant's decision

18:17.583 --> 18:23.101
to save many lives instead of
his colleague is paradoxical,

18:23.125 --> 18:27.601
but his death breathed
life to many!

18:27.625 --> 18:32.059
His indirect murder charge
is rejected.

18:32.083 --> 18:37.809
This court finds
honorable Kim innocent,

18:37.833 --> 18:42.042
as his murder charge
is completely without merit.

18:42.167 --> 18:45.792
River of Indolence

18:53.583 --> 18:54.583
Mr. Kim.

18:54.917 --> 19:00.542
The next trial determines
how well you lived your life.

19:01.125 --> 19:02.851
Whether you lived it to the fullest...

19:02.875 --> 19:03.875
Guardian Gang-lim!

19:06.542 --> 19:08.375
It's like we hit a jackpot!

19:08.583 --> 19:10.042
Finished scanning already?

19:13.458 --> 19:16.018
There is no arraignment at all,

19:16.042 --> 19:20.809
and he just has to step in
and say how hard he lived.

19:20.833 --> 19:24.934
We were even assigned
the shittiest prosecutors.

19:24.958 --> 19:26.917
To ensure Kim's smooth ride.

19:28.583 --> 19:30.500
Do not underestimate
the prosecutors.

19:31.125 --> 19:34.309
Starting off with a loss,
they'll be armed to the teeth.

19:34.333 --> 19:37.934
If they indict a paragon,
they'll get promoted.

19:37.958 --> 19:39.833
What's in it for you all?

19:44.417 --> 19:46.500
Why are you trying to
save someone like me?

19:46.833 --> 19:50.059
Don't be so cynical.

19:50.083 --> 19:51.851
Reincarnation is good for you.

19:51.875 --> 19:53.184
But I don't want
to be reincarnated.

19:53.208 --> 19:55.851
Mr. Kim, that's for
the afterlife to decide.

19:55.875 --> 19:57.292
It's a century-old promise.

20:03.167 --> 20:05.042
A promise with King Yeomra.

20:06.000 --> 20:08.809
If we help reincarnate
49 souls over a century,

20:08.833 --> 20:10.976
he'll reincarnate us as well.

20:11.000 --> 20:12.434
As whatever we want!

20:12.458 --> 20:15.643
I already decided,
son of a fortune 500 CEO.

20:15.667 --> 20:18.333
Anything else is more hell
than hell in Korea.

20:23.292 --> 20:28.018
However, that's only possible
by defending paragons like you.

20:28.042 --> 20:33.851
For a normal soul to pass
all trials in 49 days

20:33.875 --> 20:36.559
is next to impossible.

20:36.583 --> 20:40.583
Be our 48th reincarnation,
I beg of you.

20:42.250 --> 20:43.917
What if I wasn't a paragon?

20:45.208 --> 20:46.750
What would you do then?

20:47.833 --> 20:51.333
Let me stress again,
that's for the afterlife to decide.

21:11.333 --> 21:13.601
Don't look at it!

21:13.625 --> 21:14.833
No eye contact!

21:15.208 --> 21:17.667
They see people's eyes
and prey on you.

21:17.833 --> 21:21.601
They come after
souls that look at them.

21:21.625 --> 21:22.625
They'll tear you up.

21:26.375 --> 21:27.375
Mr. Kim.

21:28.000 --> 21:32.476
Think of indolence hell
as a tourist stop,

21:32.500 --> 21:34.000
but remember one thing.

21:35.542 --> 21:40.375
Do not talk back to
goddess of indolence.

21:41.458 --> 21:42.875
No exceptions.

21:43.625 --> 21:44.875
Your feet.

21:52.500 --> 21:53.500
Grab it!

21:54.375 --> 21:55.375
There, grab it!

22:04.708 --> 22:08.624
Article 2.3,
definition of indolence is,

22:08.625 --> 22:09.000
indolence hell

22:09.001 --> 22:11.832
indolence hell wasting away a
noble life given to the subject

22:11.833 --> 22:13.792
wasting away a noble life
given to the subject

22:13.958 --> 22:18.583
with endless idling
and negligence.

22:19.292 --> 22:23.101
But as you see,
indolence and laziness

22:23.125 --> 22:25.809
are inconceivable
to Kim Ja-hong.

22:25.833 --> 22:29.499
I present you his life to you,
honorable goddess.

22:29.500 --> 22:30.707
Goddess of indolence I present you
his life to you, honorable goddess.

22:30.708 --> 22:32.500
Goddess of indolence

22:34.000 --> 22:36.000
be careful!
Almost there!

22:37.625 --> 22:38.625
So close!

22:39.458 --> 22:42.684
Good! So close!
Grab it!

22:42.708 --> 22:43.708
Eh? Bee!

22:44.875 --> 22:45.875
Bee!

23:12.250 --> 23:17.726
His passion for saving lives

23:17.750 --> 23:21.625
wasn't limited to just humans!

23:29.500 --> 23:31.333
Amazing! Incredible!

23:31.792 --> 23:36.684
His affectionate gestures
reached out to

23:36.708 --> 23:40.292
even the smallest
and weakest organisms.

23:40.875 --> 23:44.351
Everything he touched,

23:44.375 --> 23:50.208
was filled with glimpses of
sacrifice and salvation.

23:50.458 --> 23:52.309
Don't look at me, look at Navi!

23:52.333 --> 23:54.768
She's over there, get her, now!

23:54.792 --> 23:57.042
Talk to her,
convince her to come.

23:57.792 --> 23:59.226
Oh gosh!

23:59.250 --> 24:03.601
His vocational ethics
that knows no boundaries

24:03.625 --> 24:09.917
often put him into
dangerous situations...

24:20.208 --> 24:21.208
Lamborghini!

24:22.042 --> 24:23.934
He's not at fault, Kim Ja-hong!

24:23.958 --> 24:26.018
We understand you, Kim Ja-hong!

24:26.042 --> 24:31.292
How could anyone
fault him for anything?

24:32.875 --> 24:33.875
Your honorable goddess.

24:34.458 --> 24:37.018
Those guardians,

24:37.042 --> 24:41.684
they're patronizing your court
by turning it into a show and tell.

24:41.708 --> 24:42.684
Hold him in contempt...

24:42.708 --> 24:43.309
Enough!

24:43.333 --> 24:44.833
Forget it, it's all settled.

24:49.333 --> 24:52.476
Let's erect his statue here.

24:52.500 --> 24:53.500
Raise it!

24:54.625 --> 24:57.292
If not for someone like him,
then who? Right?

24:57.917 --> 24:58.518
Let's erect one!

24:58.542 --> 25:00.000
Of course, your highness.

25:00.250 --> 25:03.042
While at it, a big one,
order an extra large statue.

25:05.667 --> 25:07.083
Good, something big.

25:16.167 --> 25:18.809
What compelled you

25:18.833 --> 25:21.625
to throw yourself in danger
to save others?

25:22.167 --> 25:29.375
Or did you want to live
each day to the fullest?

25:32.292 --> 25:33.542
It was all for money.

25:36.708 --> 25:37.708
Say what?

25:41.958 --> 25:43.250
Did I hear money?

25:44.125 --> 25:45.125
Cash?

25:46.167 --> 25:47.167
Money?

25:49.792 --> 25:52.768
Yes, I...

25:52.792 --> 25:53.684
Had to make money.

25:53.708 --> 25:54.708
Mr. Kim!

25:57.875 --> 25:58.875
Your highness,

25:59.375 --> 26:01.708
we'll start the lift.

26:02.250 --> 26:04.559
Sure, go on.

26:04.583 --> 26:05.583
Okay.

26:06.125 --> 26:08.042
Was money god to you?

26:10.625 --> 26:12.708
You served a terrible god.

26:15.458 --> 26:20.708
I'll make you feel sorry
for choosing the money god.

27:01.292 --> 27:03.250
Hewonmak!
Go save him!

27:07.000 --> 27:08.000
He's gonna fall!

27:13.500 --> 27:14.500
Merciful goddess!

27:14.750 --> 27:16.792
I beg of you to look at
the mirror of Karma!

27:16.917 --> 27:18.500
What do you think you're doing?!

27:19.000 --> 27:21.083
He worshipped the wrong god!

27:21.833 --> 27:23.268
Yes, he did.

27:23.292 --> 27:25.809
And for that reason,

27:25.833 --> 27:29.250
he extinguished fire during the day
and light one at night.

27:29.833 --> 27:31.250
Get him charcoal fire!

27:32.000 --> 27:33.000
Sure!

27:35.042 --> 27:36.393
Watch out, fire coming through.

27:36.417 --> 27:38.893
Due to utter poverty,

27:38.917 --> 27:42.518
Kim delivered veggies
on his off days,

27:42.542 --> 27:44.893
and cleaned sauna floors
on the weekends,

27:44.917 --> 27:46.893
and when that was over,

27:46.917 --> 27:50.833
he was forced to work
as a temp driver.

28:00.708 --> 28:01.708
Ja-hong!

28:01.958 --> 28:03.750
You bastard!

28:04.250 --> 28:05.667
Drive straight!

28:11.625 --> 28:12.708
Even day offs?

28:13.417 --> 28:16.476
Then when did he get any rest?

28:16.500 --> 28:18.601
His true day off

28:18.625 --> 28:21.934
was the day after his death.

28:21.958 --> 28:26.458
He has not rested for
a moment when he was alive.

28:27.292 --> 28:29.768
His ailing mother
required treatment,

28:29.792 --> 28:34.042
and his brother's law school
wasn't cheap!

28:35.333 --> 28:39.708
Without Kim's money,
they wouldn't have survived!

28:40.958 --> 28:44.083
Money was everything to him!

28:46.125 --> 28:50.518
He was only able to sever
the reach of this god by dying!

28:50.542 --> 28:53.309
I beg of you to
embrace this soul,

28:53.333 --> 28:57.125
a soul that only looked after
his poverty-stricken family!

29:01.708 --> 29:02.708
Thank you.

29:02.917 --> 29:03.917
Good afternoon.

29:07.833 --> 29:09.958
My verdict is as follows.

29:13.500 --> 29:19.143
The defendant's reason for
not being indolent

29:19.167 --> 29:24.059
was said to be accumulation
of money and goods,

29:24.083 --> 29:28.726
which were not for
his own selfish interest,

29:28.750 --> 29:33.332
but to support his ailing mother
and his young brother,

29:33.333 --> 29:35.416
blade forest but to support his
ailing mother and his young brother,

29:35.417 --> 29:36.707
blade forest
I find the defendant not guilty.

29:36.708 --> 29:39.667
I find the defendant not guilty.

29:44.500 --> 29:49.268
Deceit hell judges the lies
one said in his life.

29:49.292 --> 29:52.476
Branches are razor sharp,
hence blade forest.

29:52.500 --> 29:55.000
The reflection of the moon
on the blades...

29:55.667 --> 29:57.726
Is quite beautiful, right?

29:57.750 --> 30:00.333
But if you touch anything
out of your curiosity...

30:01.708 --> 30:03.958
If you did out of curiosity,

30:10.333 --> 30:14.833
The blades will slice you open
and you'll feel incredible pain.

30:15.333 --> 30:18.083
I begged you not to
talk back at the goddess.

30:18.333 --> 30:19.875
You broke my promise again.

30:20.708 --> 30:23.184
I won't be making
any more of those.

30:23.208 --> 30:24.792
It'll be orders from here on.

30:27.792 --> 30:28.792
Free him!

30:29.042 --> 30:31.518
Why are you so rebellious?

30:31.542 --> 30:33.208
It'd be nice if you do
what you're told.

30:33.792 --> 30:38.250
We get a 48th paragon and
you get a reincarnation.

30:40.042 --> 30:43.851
And get a dream visitation
before reincarnation.

30:43.875 --> 30:46.351
You could appear
in your Mom's dream.

30:46.375 --> 30:49.708
Please hold on,
it'll heal shortly.

30:50.500 --> 30:51.750
What did you say?

30:52.167 --> 30:54.309
Wounds heal faster in afterlife...

30:54.333 --> 30:57.226
No, dream visitation?

30:57.250 --> 31:00.518
You don't know?
Appearing in dreams.

31:00.542 --> 31:04.625
It's a privilege given to those
who receive reincarnation.

31:05.250 --> 31:07.500
Really? I can meet my mother?

31:09.333 --> 31:11.184
I thought we told you.

31:11.208 --> 31:15.601
Before you reincarnate,
you're allowed to see anyone

31:15.625 --> 31:17.518
to say farewell one last time...

31:17.542 --> 31:21.143
People who say they met their
dead father in a dream,

31:21.167 --> 31:23.125
that's what this is.

31:28.875 --> 31:29.875
What's with him?

31:31.042 --> 31:32.042
Mother!

31:33.625 --> 31:34.684
Mother!

31:34.708 --> 31:37.309
Yes, Ja-hong,
it's me, your mother.

31:37.333 --> 31:38.333
Mother...

31:38.500 --> 31:40.917
Stay in character?
Sure, sure.

31:44.208 --> 31:45.208
Mother...

31:49.458 --> 31:50.458
Damn.

31:52.000 --> 31:54.643
This place feels eerie,
even after a century.

31:54.667 --> 31:56.583
We could just walk...

31:57.208 --> 32:01.625
Kiddo, explain this to him
so he doesn't screw us up again.

32:02.750 --> 32:06.059
Think of this as
a special treat for the paragon.

32:06.083 --> 32:09.625
It's a fast transportation system
to pass through this area.

32:16.833 --> 32:17.833
What's he up to?

32:24.625 --> 32:25.625
Let's gel going-

32:50.875 --> 32:53.542
Hell ghoul?
Why is that here?!

32:55.583 --> 32:56.583
Dammit...

32:57.583 --> 32:59.333
Even the time is speeding up!

33:00.125 --> 33:01.768
From the living world...

33:01.792 --> 33:03.208
Is it a vengeful spirit?

33:03.833 --> 33:06.833
Got anymore immediate family
in the living world?

33:26.042 --> 33:27.768
Drastic changes in the afterlife

33:27.792 --> 33:30.708
means your family member
has become a vengeful spirit.

33:33.667 --> 33:34.917
I don't understand...

33:35.333 --> 33:36.333
Sir!

33:38.375 --> 33:39.375
The head!

33:41.208 --> 33:42.208
Get rid of it!

33:56.917 --> 33:58.583
Captain! Pull yourself up!

34:18.417 --> 34:19.268
Cap, you okay?

34:19.292 --> 34:21.351
There!
What?

34:21.375 --> 34:22.476
Smash it!

34:22.500 --> 34:23.500
Smash the column!

34:26.375 --> 34:27.792
Hurry! Please!

35:13.250 --> 35:14.500
Don't understand?

35:14.833 --> 35:17.268
Either your mother or brother!

35:17.292 --> 35:19.976
Somebody has died with a grudge!

35:20.000 --> 35:22.893
And became a vengeful spirit!

35:22.917 --> 35:28.250
With that roaming the living world,
the afterlife has gone to shit!

35:32.125 --> 35:33.125
Mother...

35:33.833 --> 35:35.208
Mama's boy...

35:36.250 --> 35:39.167
Deok-choon, put a blind on him.

35:39.542 --> 35:40.500
Hurry!

35:45.000 --> 35:48.018
Could something have
happened to her?

35:48.042 --> 35:50.934
We're not sure,
but I doubt that.

35:50.958 --> 35:52.934
Please, I need a firm answer!

35:52.958 --> 35:54.184
Is she alright?

35:54.208 --> 35:56.184
You want a firm answer?

35:56.208 --> 35:57.684
Your trial or not,

35:57.708 --> 36:01.434
if hell ghouls are wreaking havoc
and the time has speed up,

36:01.458 --> 36:07.833
we'll never reach the final trial
in 49 days at this rate.

36:10.250 --> 36:12.958
Deok-choon!
Guardian Lee Deok-choon!

36:23.458 --> 36:24.458
Deok-choon.

36:25.333 --> 36:28.393
I'm gonna take a detour,
take over for a bit.

36:28.417 --> 36:31.976
He's a paragon so there won't
be any victims.

36:32.000 --> 36:34.018
If there's a problem,

36:34.042 --> 36:36.625
stall the trial until I signal.

36:38.917 --> 36:40.184
I'm counting on you.

36:40.208 --> 36:43.226
Don't forget that
you and I are linked.

36:43.250 --> 36:44.934
Don't worry, cap.

36:44.958 --> 36:46.018
I'm here.

36:46.042 --> 36:48.143
No, I don't want you to think.

36:48.167 --> 36:49.601
Do me a favor.

36:49.625 --> 36:51.143
Whenever you get an idea,

36:51.167 --> 36:54.768
make sure to doubt it
before acting on it.

36:54.792 --> 36:57.684
If it's good,
then verify with her.

36:57.708 --> 36:59.934
Correct him instantly.

36:59.958 --> 37:01.768
Easy, eh?
It should be.

37:01.792 --> 37:07.417
So aside from protecting Kim,
I don't want you to think.

37:09.667 --> 37:11.083
It's my Sincere hope.

37:12.750 --> 37:13.750
Okay?

37:16.083 --> 37:17.083
Good.

37:47.792 --> 37:50.583
Items of the deceased
accepted by: Kim Su-Hong, brother.

38:03.458 --> 38:05.458
These are Ja-hong's
personal items.

38:16.500 --> 38:17.500
Mom!

38:20.167 --> 38:22.458
Why do you take that?

38:22.750 --> 38:24.833
It's dead!
Throw it away!

38:34.917 --> 38:37.226
My mother is a mute.

38:37.250 --> 38:39.601
She can't talk.

38:39.625 --> 38:46.375
I've never heard her voice
since I was born.

39:36.292 --> 39:37.833
Just wait 2 weeks.

39:38.792 --> 39:40.958
After my discharge,
I'll always stay with you.

39:46.417 --> 39:48.833
Kim Ja-Hong, that bastard!

40:04.333 --> 40:05.875
Who are you?

40:19.667 --> 40:21.125
My deepest condolences, Ma'am.

40:24.958 --> 40:28.851
Mr. Kim saved my life,

40:28.875 --> 40:31.208
I was given a new life
because of him.

40:36.167 --> 40:41.333
I saw the news on TV
and came right away.

40:42.208 --> 40:44.042
I wanted to say farewell...

41:03.458 --> 41:08.958
I haven't had a chance
to say good bye.

41:09.750 --> 41:15.518
If it's not too much trouble,

41:15.542 --> 41:17.792
may I do so privately?

41:27.000 --> 41:28.250
Thank you, Ma'am.

41:33.542 --> 41:34.542
Kim Su-Hong.

41:37.083 --> 41:38.583
Where is the place
of your death?

42:51.208 --> 42:55.875
I must be close to my death.

42:57.208 --> 42:59.583
I can see the grim reaper.

43:00.167 --> 43:02.750
Don't say that!

43:03.333 --> 43:07.167
You're not gonna die, grandpa!

43:22.792 --> 43:24.542
Look at the sky.

43:25.208 --> 43:26.851
Is this the afterlife or a club?

43:26.875 --> 43:28.792
How does the time
pass so quickly?

43:35.542 --> 43:37.458
No tickling.

43:39.333 --> 43:40.333
Excuse me.

43:41.292 --> 43:42.684
Any news of my mother?

43:42.708 --> 43:44.208
No tickling.

43:44.875 --> 43:46.833
Excuse me? Wake up!

43:48.042 --> 43:51.768
Don't disturb her,
she's not taking a nap!

43:51.792 --> 43:55.351
She's looking up
next trial's charges!

43:55.375 --> 43:57.625
You really don't get it,
are you dumb?

43:57.875 --> 44:00.417
Why did you take that off?
Put it back on!

44:05.583 --> 44:07.750
Forget it, it's too late.

44:08.125 --> 44:11.000
Get up, wake her up too.

44:11.667 --> 44:13.458
Open your eyes!
Hurry, come on.

44:15.250 --> 44:17.000
Is it over?

44:18.042 --> 44:19.375
Yeah, over for us.

44:52.667 --> 44:53.667
It's King Yeomra!

45:11.958 --> 45:13.333
Bow, bow!

45:13.750 --> 45:14.833
Bow your head!

45:18.250 --> 45:22.458
He's already dead,
but does he wish to die again?

45:23.083 --> 45:26.125
He's the first paragon
in 19 years, majesty!

45:28.750 --> 45:32.226
And why does our honorable guest

45:32.250 --> 45:35.268
bring forth hell ghouls
and disturb my realm?

45:35.292 --> 45:38.101
Guardian Gang-lim has
gone down to investigate.

45:38.125 --> 45:41.292
He's going as fast as he can,
your majesty.

45:41.542 --> 45:43.809
How will he calm the spirit?

45:43.833 --> 45:47.143
The body will be burned
and its soul eliminated,

45:47.167 --> 45:50.125
but without disturbing
order of the living world.

45:52.375 --> 45:53.375
No!

45:56.125 --> 45:57.143
No!

45:57.167 --> 45:57.684
Hold.

45:57.708 --> 45:58.958
No, you bastards!

45:59.542 --> 46:00.833
' No!
' Stop!

46:01.167 --> 46:02.583
You can't do that!
Please stop!

46:04.458 --> 46:05.458
Stop!

46:05.667 --> 46:08.833
Who the hell are you?
Answer me!

46:09.167 --> 46:11.000
Don't you dare touch my mother!

46:11.458 --> 46:12.875
I'll beat the hell out of you!

46:13.333 --> 46:14.393
Get him off.
I'm so sorry!

46:14.417 --> 46:15.893
Who the hell are you?

46:15.917 --> 46:17.768
How dare you
eliminate my mother!

46:17.792 --> 46:19.583
Get him off of me.

46:20.917 --> 46:22.292
Do you know her?!

46:22.458 --> 46:23.958
Don't pretend to be cool!
I'm sorry!

46:24.333 --> 46:27.083
My apologies, your majesty!

46:28.417 --> 46:29.625
Calm down!

46:31.083 --> 46:32.292
Hold still!

46:35.917 --> 46:37.125
Shut up!

46:37.833 --> 46:39.042
Shut the hell up!

46:39.917 --> 46:41.750
Please give us more time,
honorable king!

46:46.625 --> 46:50.851
Go tell Gang-lim,
if he eliminates the...

46:50.875 --> 46:52.625
Don't bullshit me!

46:54.833 --> 46:56.167
What's with him?

46:58.042 --> 46:59.768
Go tell Gang-lim!

46:59.792 --> 47:02.643
If he doesn't eliminate
the vengeful spirit soon,

47:02.667 --> 47:04.958
I'll go down to
the living world myself!

47:05.833 --> 47:07.083
Yes, your majesty!

47:09.625 --> 47:10.643
My ap0logies!

47:10.667 --> 47:11.667
What the hell are you?!

47:11.917 --> 47:12.917
I'm so sorry!

47:19.583 --> 47:23.643
Is it true that Sgt. Kim
deserted because of his brother?

47:23.667 --> 47:24.143
I dunno...

47:24.167 --> 47:24.934
Do you know anything?

47:24.958 --> 47:27.042
He deserted?
It's been 3 days.

47:28.167 --> 47:31.917
Why'd he desert
just before his discharge?

47:34.208 --> 47:36.726
I feel so bad...

47:36.750 --> 47:39.059
If it was me, my guts would rot.

47:39.083 --> 47:41.000
And full of fucking maggots.

48:01.250 --> 48:04.458
I'll ask you again, who was it?

48:04.750 --> 48:05.726
Sorry, sir!

48:05.750 --> 48:08.458
Buddy, look at his face.

48:09.333 --> 48:12.458
I'll do the same to you
and go to military prison.

48:13.667 --> 48:14.476
I'm sorry!
Sorry, sir!

48:14.500 --> 48:16.667
He's on a suicide watch!

48:17.417 --> 48:22.809
Something over my heart!

48:22.833 --> 48:23.833
Very nice!

48:24.125 --> 48:28.434
A watch badge!

48:28.458 --> 48:30.434
My lyrics are so good!

48:30.458 --> 48:32.434
I wrote it for you, dude!

48:32.458 --> 48:33.917
I love it, sir.

48:35.625 --> 48:39.893
Dong-yeon, get up, dude.

48:39.917 --> 48:42.018
Sir, I can't walk any further.

48:42.042 --> 48:43.042
Of course you can.

48:44.167 --> 48:45.434
Get up, come on.
I'm so exhausted.

48:45.458 --> 48:47.042
You can do this.

48:54.833 --> 48:57.851
It's not that,
I can't sleep at all.

48:57.875 --> 49:01.750
So why can't you?

49:02.875 --> 49:05.917
It feels like someone's
watching me at night,

49:07.833 --> 49:09.333
and I get the chills...

49:11.750 --> 49:13.208
Lieutenant! Salute!

49:14.542 --> 49:17.458
An investigator's here
about Sgt. Kim's desertion.

49:17.875 --> 49:18.958
Is that so?

49:19.708 --> 49:20.958
They sent a it. Colonel.

49:22.458 --> 49:24.458
HQ investigator?
Yes, sir.

49:29.292 --> 49:32.625
Deceit Hell

49:43.250 --> 49:47.309
“Dad will always watch you
from somewhere nearby.”

49:47.333 --> 49:53.601
“So study hard and become
a good person.

49:53.625 --> 49:54.167
If you're a good girl,
over the Christmas...”

49:54.168 --> 49:57.124
Goddess of deceit if you're a
good girl, over the Christmas...”

49:57.125 --> 49:57.542
Goddess of deceit what's that?

49:57.542 --> 49:58.125
What's that?

49:58.708 --> 50:02.059
Kim wrote a letter
to the dead colleague's kid.

50:02.083 --> 50:03.184
As her Dad...

50:03.208 --> 50:05.542
“We'll go to
Disney land together.

50:06.375 --> 50:07.958
I'm so sorry,

50:08.458 --> 50:09.542
and I love you.”

50:09.958 --> 50:10.958
The dead man?

50:11.667 --> 50:13.018
Isn't that the will, then?

50:13.042 --> 50:16.458
That's forgery of
a private document!

50:16.792 --> 50:21.375
“Don't get sick
and always be healthy.”

50:22.125 --> 50:27.851
This is just a sample
of defendant's fake letters.

50:27.875 --> 50:34.351
Before this court validates
the nature of his crime,

50:34.375 --> 50:38.458
I'd like you to pay attention
to the sheer amount of letters.

50:44.292 --> 50:45.643
How many did he write?

50:45.667 --> 50:47.083
98 letters!

50:47.667 --> 50:51.018
That's the number of letters
this “paragon”

50:51.042 --> 50:56.208
sent under the pretense
of giving hope!

50:57.583 --> 51:00.333
98? That many?

51:01.000 --> 51:03.792
Why didn't he write 2 more
and make it a 100?

51:04.708 --> 51:06.208
Are you insane?!

51:14.625 --> 51:16.042
Answer, defendant.

51:16.458 --> 51:20.042
Your legal representative
asked you if you're insane.

51:23.958 --> 51:25.875
My heart ached so much...

51:31.333 --> 51:32.917
They were too young.

51:37.458 --> 51:39.042
Much too young...

51:43.042 --> 51:44.500
That was the only thing...

51:46.708 --> 51:48.333
I could do for them...

52:27.208 --> 52:28.792
Salute!
At ease.

52:30.667 --> 52:34.250
I won't mince words,
let's cut to the chase.

52:35.042 --> 52:39.184
Sgt. Kim has deserted
but his family doesn't know yet?

52:39.208 --> 52:42.018
It's only been a few weeks
since his brother died.

52:42.042 --> 52:44.893
He could be hiding
in the barracks,

52:44.917 --> 52:45.917
but most of all,

52:46.375 --> 52:49.667
his mother could
go into shock...

52:52.250 --> 52:53.667
Your compassion brings
tears to my eyes.

52:54.333 --> 52:56.125
What's with the bullshit?

52:58.417 --> 53:01.833
Sgt. Kim was like
my own brother.

53:02.417 --> 53:07.143
Unlike others his age,
he looked after his men,

53:07.167 --> 53:10.042
and thanks to him
I received some commendation.

53:11.125 --> 53:15.708
We will be contacting
his mother soon.

53:18.042 --> 53:19.833
Where did you bury him?

53:21.625 --> 53:23.500
Defendant, please answer.

53:25.000 --> 53:26.917
Do you refuse to answer?

53:29.958 --> 53:30.958
Defendant!

53:31.458 --> 53:35.351
Her majesty is asking you
if you didn't know about

53:35.375 --> 53:39.518
their pain and despair
upon discovering the truth!

53:39.542 --> 53:41.542
Please answer!

53:42.375 --> 53:47.018
She knew the letters were fake,
but she still waited everyday,

53:47.042 --> 53:49.375
rain or shine, day or night!

53:50.125 --> 53:52.375
Is the defendant
refusing to testify?

53:56.125 --> 53:58.809
You may think that silence
is the best defense,

53:58.833 --> 54:03.333
but I'll gladly cut off
your useless tongue.

54:13.458 --> 54:14.458
Sir!

54:15.042 --> 54:17.292
Cap! Cap!

54:17.875 --> 54:18.875
Captain!

54:20.875 --> 54:22.125
I'm a busy man.

54:23.583 --> 54:24.792
For the last time,

54:26.125 --> 54:27.500
where did you bury him?

54:32.208 --> 54:33.208
Please!

54:36.292 --> 54:42.125
I'll accuse you to the mp
for false information!

54:45.958 --> 54:47.000
That's enough.

54:47.875 --> 54:48.875
No need for that.

54:50.167 --> 54:52.708
Is Kim's last duty report correct?

54:53.208 --> 54:56.250
Kim had a night guard duty
with pvt. Won dong-yeon.

55:04.417 --> 55:05.667
I gave you a chance.

55:06.625 --> 55:07.958
Watch your tongue later.

55:12.125 --> 55:13.458
Assistant guardian
Lee Deok-choon!

55:15.083 --> 55:16.809
No! Not yet!

55:16.833 --> 55:17.833
Assistant guardian
Lee Deok-choon!

55:18.333 --> 55:19.667
Lee Deok-choon reporting!

55:20.333 --> 55:21.333
Initiate link.

55:25.292 --> 55:28.500
I'll now begin our final defense.

55:36.458 --> 55:37.542
Hold on for a bit.

55:40.500 --> 55:42.643
Your highness.
Your highness.

55:42.667 --> 55:45.768
Defendant Kim Ja-Hong
is indeed a liar.

55:45.792 --> 55:47.458
Is indeed a liar.

55:54.708 --> 55:58.643
What you're seeing now is

55:58.667 --> 56:02.059
not only fake letters
to Ji-yeon, who lost her Dad,

56:02.083 --> 56:05.559
but also fake letters to his mother
for the past 15 years.

56:05.583 --> 56:07.333
For the past 15 years.

56:08.958 --> 56:10.750
What the heck?

56:11.417 --> 56:12.750
Shoo! Go away!

56:15.792 --> 56:16.792
Here he comes!

56:19.583 --> 56:20.583
Catch him!

56:28.833 --> 56:34.000
Mother, I injured my arm
while playing with my son.

56:34.458 --> 56:38.893
He lied about a boar injury
as his son's playful trick.

56:38.917 --> 56:41.809
My wife made scorched rice today.

56:41.833 --> 56:46.101
Fearing that his mother would
give up fighting her illness,

56:46.125 --> 56:51.375
he breathed hope into her
by creating a wife.

56:52.500 --> 56:54.476
Then what happened?

56:54.500 --> 56:57.309
His mother overcame
her incurable illness,

56:57.333 --> 57:01.917
made a full recovery!
And leads a fulfilling life!

57:06.000 --> 57:06.792
Mom, try it.

57:08.167 --> 57:08.476
Is it good?

57:08.500 --> 57:11.893
If she knew how he braved death

57:11.917 --> 57:17.934
to earn money and pay
for her hospital bills,

57:17.958 --> 57:21.559
I'd like to ask if her recovery
would've been possible.

57:21.583 --> 57:23.768
If she ever found out!

57:23.792 --> 57:29.143
That all those letters were lies,
imagine her despair,

57:29.167 --> 57:31.809
and would that be treatable?!

57:31.833 --> 57:36.458
I'd like to add that
everyone grew with despair.

57:36.750 --> 57:38.500
One last question.

57:39.417 --> 57:43.583
Do you deny writing
all of these fake letters?

57:43.958 --> 57:47.101
With the anticipation
and hope in those letters,

57:47.125 --> 57:49.976
their sense of loss
would've been equally great.

57:50.000 --> 57:52.268
But they!
Those of the living!

57:52.292 --> 57:57.000
They grew up
as much as their loss.

57:58.792 --> 58:01.726
My dear daddy!
Are you doing well?

58:01.750 --> 58:05.726
Your firefighter friends are
taking good care of us.

58:05.750 --> 58:08.101
I'm doing well in school...

58:08.125 --> 58:11.684
I can do laundry and
make dinner too.

58:11.708 --> 58:14.851
You may be away,
but you're always in my heart.

58:14.875 --> 58:17.059
Watch over me forever.

58:17.083 --> 58:19.208
Your Jewel, Ji-yeon.

58:41.625 --> 58:44.476
Prosecution,

58:44.500 --> 58:47.250
were there any
similar cases in the past?

58:47.375 --> 58:50.184
No, well...

58:50.208 --> 58:51.643
The admiral!

58:51.667 --> 58:54.583
Admiral Yi said
not to announce his death.

58:57.292 --> 58:59.934
To the enemy forces,
of course...

58:59.958 --> 59:01.393
It was a strategic tactic...

59:01.417 --> 59:03.792
The admiral said that
to his allies.

59:04.458 --> 59:07.375
So that his men kept
their morale high.

59:07.792 --> 59:08.875
This is why...

59:10.208 --> 59:13.768
I ordered all paragons to
just pass through

59:13.792 --> 59:15.250
