59:16.833 --> 59:19.726
In the case of defendant
Kim Ja-hong's fake letters,

59:19.750 --> 59:24.476
this court will dismiss
all charges against him.

59:24.500 --> 59:29.226
Any pieces of evidence
presented today here

59:29.250 --> 59:33.601
are removed and all charges
are dropped immediately,

59:33.625 --> 59:35.958
and he may proceed
to the next trial.

59:36.917 --> 59:39.000
