01:02:22.125 --> 01:02:23.458
Listen up.

01:02:24.000 --> 01:02:26.458
His brother is dead and
became the vengeful spirit.

01:02:27.208 --> 01:02:29.625
I'm looking into where
and how he died,

01:02:30.708 --> 01:02:33.208
