01:09:20.957 --> 01:09:23.559
Listen to me, okay?

01:09:23.582 --> 01:09:26.000
Dong-yeon, look at me,
you didn't do it on purpose.

01:09:26.292 --> 01:09:28.059
It's okay,
I can take care of it.

01:09:28.082 --> 01:09:30.332
My promotion
is next month, asshole!

01:09:46.082 --> 01:09:50.167
